ca.mcgill.ecse321.scorekeeper.model

Class Team

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.mcgill.ecse321.scorekeeper.model.Team

  • public class Team
extends java.lang.Object
    Domain object that stores data relating to Teams. Teams contain Players, and two Teams play a Game. Teams also belong to a League
    See Also:
    Players, Game, League
